node.text: These 4 walls, they hold laughter, joy, sadness, pain, victory, defeat, creativity, love and so much more, these 4 walls hold me up, these 4 walls give life to so many and enrich those who dare to step inside. A barbershop is so much more than a place to get a haircut, this is therapy, celebration, comfort, bonding, this is a community! I hold these 4 walls so tight because to me they are sacred!

node.text: The final product! I can not be more excited or say enough amazing things about my boy @ryansavagedds #savagesmile

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by California Barber - Vinnie ✪ in Orange, California. May be an image of 3 people, people standing and outdoors.

node.text: Through think and thin, the 3 of us will always have each other! The greatest 4 years of my life are because of this beautiful little angel, the honor of being your father is more than words, I can’t not wait to see what you give to the world! I love you to the moon and back my gorgeous little love! Happy Birthday princess!

node.text: Do you get to do what you love everyday? If you do, do you understand how lucky you are? If you don’t, why not? Wake up and push everyday until you get to do what you love! What do you love to do?
